title: GAME RECAP: Lakers 103, Warriors 100
description: The Lakers defeated the Warriors, 103-100. title: First ElektroMOD: Opel Manta GSe Premiere
description:
50 years after it took the world by storm, Opel Manta is once again in pioneering form, as the first electric restomod in the history of a German car brand. https://www.opel.com/concept-cars/manta-gse-elektromod.html

Manta is again in top form, as the first electric MOD in the history of Opel. With a full-battery powertrain delivering 108 kW/147 hp of rear-wheel drive power and the original four-speed gearbox it is a thrilling example of Opel pioneering electrification concepts. A special Pixel Vizor stretches across the full width, letting this Manta talk to the world. 

The new Opel Manta GSe ElektroMOD combines the best of both worlds: the classic appearance of a style icon together with state-of-the-art technology for sustainable motoring: the new Manta is future-proof: electric, emissions-free and full of emotions.

The Manta GSe impressively demonstrates the enthusiasm with which we build cars at Opel. It combines our great Opel tradition with today's commitment to emissions-free mobility for a very desirable, sustainable future. Opel is already electric with many models ‚Äì and now the legendary Manta is too.

It reflects the fascination of a growing fan community that transforms classic cars like the Manta into so-called RestoMods with modern technologies. It features our new, bold and pure design and comes as purely battery-electric which makes the Manta as sporty as a genuine Opel GSe and proudly displays our ambitions in its name ‚Äì ElektroMOD.

Die Bundeswehr kann dadurch rund um die Uhr auf zwei Transportflugzeuge des Typs Antonow-124-100 zur√ºckgreifen, die auf dem Flughafen Leipzig stationiert sind. Mit der Antonov, dem gr√∂√üten Transportflugzeug der Welt, k√∂nnen Hubschrauber, Panzer oder zum Beispiel Lastwagen trotz ihres hohen Gewichtes und der Gr√∂√üe sicher transportiert werden.
Der SALIS-Vertrag, √ºber den die Bundeswehr auf die Antonows in Leipzig zur√ºckgreifen kann, wurde gemeinsam von 10 Nationen der NATO und der EU mit einem zivilen Auftragnehmer geschlossen.
